4 月 29 日。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 05:15:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/bond-trustee-becomes-new-petitioner-liquidate-china-developer-kaisa-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>阿里巴巴旗下灵犀游戏表示，管理层将辞职，为年轻高管让路</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/alibabas-lingxi-games-says-management-step-down-make-way-younger-execs-2024-03-08/</link><description>一份内部备忘录显示，阿里巴巴集团旗下视频游戏部门灵犀游戏已告知员工，其领导团队将辞职，为更年轻的管理层让路。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 05:12:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/alibabas-lingxi-games-says-management-step-down-make-way-younger-execs-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>彭博社报道，华为、中芯国际使用美国技术制造先进芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-smic-used-us-tech-make-advanced-chips-bloomberg-reports-2024-03-08/</link><description>据彭博社援引知情人士的话报道，中国公司华为技术有限公司和中芯国际公司将于 2023 年使用美国技术在中国生产先进芯片。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 02:50:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-smic-used-us-tech-make-advanced-chips-bloomberg-reports-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>美国就业数据公布前亚洲股市创七个月新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-08/</link><description>周五，亚洲股市上涨至七个月高点，追随全球股市走势，因投资者对主要央行主导的即将到来的降息周期前景感到乐观，美元和国债收益率承压。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 02:33:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国海油在南海发现亿吨级油田</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-cnooc-makes-100-million-ton-oilfield-discovery-south-china-sea-2024-03-08/</link><description>中国国有石油天然气巨头中海油周五在一份声明中表示，该公司在南海发现了一个新的储量，探明储量超过 1 亿吨石油当量。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 02:03:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-cnooc-makes-100-million-ton-oilfield-discovery-south-china-sea-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国最高立法者承诺维护主权和安全利益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-top-legislators-safeguard-sovereignty-security-interests-2024-03-08/</link><description>中国最高立法委员周五誓言要制定一系列新法律，以“实现国家安全制度和能力现代化”，维护国家主权利益。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 01:23:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-top-legislators-safeguard-sovereignty-security-interests-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>关键就业数据公布前美元下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-droops-ahead-payrolls-2024-03-08/</link><description>周五，由于美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔对未来几个月降息更有信心，美元迎来今年最大单周跌幅，而日元则因日本加息的猜测不断升温而上涨。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 01:12:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-droops-ahead-payrolls-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>香港颁布新国安法 刑期更严厉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-government-issues-draft-new-national-security-law-2024-03-08/</link><description>香港周五公布了新的国家安全法草案，一些律师表示，这份文件扩大了可被视为煽动叛乱和国家机密的范围，对犯有这些罪行的任何人以及其他几人都给予更严厉的处罚。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 00:38:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-government-issues-draft-new-national-security-law-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰推动和平计划，指出朝鲜参与与中国特使的会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-presses-peace-plan-points-n-korean-involvement-talks-with-chinese-envoy-2024-03-07/</link><description>乌克兰高级官员在周四与中国地区特使会面时，敦促基辅结束与俄罗斯长达两年的冲突的计划，并提交了他们所说的朝鲜向莫斯科提供武器的证据。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 23:25:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-presses-peace-plan-points-n-korean-involvement-talks-with-chinese-envoy-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>美国陆军情报分析师被控向中国出售军事机密</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-army-intelligence-analyst-charged-with-selling-military-secrets-china-2024-03-07/</link><description>一名美国陆军情报分析员周四被捕，被指控密谋向中国出售敏感国防信息。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 22:10:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-army-intelligence-analyst-charged-with-selling-military-secrets-china-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>早盘：全球市场阳光刺破中国乌云</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-07/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 21:50:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>参议院民主党人敦促拜登政府提高对中国电动汽车的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/senate-democrats-urge-biden-administration-hike-tariffs-chinese-evs-2024-03-07/</link><description>来自汽车制造州的三名参议院民主党人周四敦促拜登政府提高对中国电动汽车的进口关税，以应对国家安全风险，这是立法者保护美国汽车行业的最新举措。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 18:14:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/senate-democrats-urge-biden-administration-hike-tariffs-chinese-evs-2024-03-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>